{
  "stem": "25773.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you should try to-- you have the shelter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, anyway, then my step--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's Michael, this friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then-- and Rosa gradually said, look, you should go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because maybe you could make your way to this little villa we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe somebody will be saved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe somebody you can help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know, this was-- it was a terrible decision.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that is, you know, something which one never forgets, this very, very traumatic experience, when you have to make a choice between life and death, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was, you know, very tragic that I couldn't save Rosa-- never mind the others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tried my best for everybody, for all the-- for my father, for Michael, for Rudolph.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did-- but not for Rosa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was anyway downhearted already with the-- with the loss of her husband, the loss of the son--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[? --and ?] [? things ?] [? like ?] that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, one day, I-- and she was with-- she moved to her cousin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you could move to the premises.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had a cousin, what I mentioned before, was a very nice lady.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, look, I'll be with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever happens, we'll be together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to-- left the ghetto for-- left-- left the ghetto for good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Went to my cousin--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- yes, this was a very tragic, very terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this Michael tried again and again to smuggle Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he did smuggle a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, when I was already on the Christian side, I one day telephoned from a safe telephone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the father answered--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
